'''Thi Sawrtin''' was a veteran [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] when he met newbie [[Zayl Braith]]. Sawrtin accepted her as a partner and they began working together in many smuggling runs.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

At some point before 1 ABY, during a "routine" run through the [[Noonian sector/Legends|Noonian sector]], Sawrtin and Braith found an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Immobilizer 418 Interdictor-class Heavy Cruiser|Interdictor cruiser]], the ''[[Tory's Catcher]]'', and were captured. Sawrtin found that Imperial Captain [[Gresia Vleen]] was not a friend of bribes. Vleen shot Sawrtin, impounded the smuggler's ship and imprisoned Braith.<ref name="AIR" />

